This preamplifier was designed By Shahar Levi for personal use.

The preamplifier was tested on the "BM800" Condenser Microphone and is suppose to be good for other models.
In general this is a Balanced TO Unbalanced audio converter with Pahntom Power.

Recommended input voltage is between 30-48 volts DC.

Potentiometer:
VR1 - Gain.
VR2 - Volume.
